{"tid":2505083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八達通將分階段將儲值額自動增加至3000元","createTime":"2021-04-26T10:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T10:42:06.000Z","uid":229904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d58a5ee82254381f8060176a0c143332792a3f32","tid":2505083,"uid":229904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"於2019年12月1日前發出的八達通卡及產品，儲值限額為1000元。八達通指，持卡人周四起，透過八達通手機程式查閱紀錄及餘額，或領取交通補貼後，卡內的儲值限額會自動提升至3000元。<br />\n<br />\n持卡人下月16日起，在交通補貼領取機便利店或超市，成功領取補貼或增值後，儲值限額亦會自動提升至3000元<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n八達通指，自動提升儲值限額是為持卡人日後各類型消費作準備，八達通早前獲政府甄選為，協助發放5000元消費券的電子支付工具之一。<br />\n<br />\n八達通將分階段自動將儲值額增至3000元<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=432540&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432540%26refer%3DShare&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B65S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=62eeb4c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432540%26refer%3DShare&h=6f7c35bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=432540&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"b566188ff489e76625547e884158642c94f54acd","tid":2505083,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"我自己已加到3000"},{"pid":"7f1a8d70b107cc9fd0f19e3ded812f9325993da0","tid":2505083,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"5000最後都係拎黎返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb2c5b4ca08f9bb94eac5893e2fabe7187e90b5","tid":2505083,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1a8d70b107cc9fd0f19e3ded812f9325993da0","tid":2505083,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"5000最後都係拎黎返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:42:06.